libtime
=========================================================================

Copyright (c) 1997,2012 by Thomas Forbriger (BFO Schiltach)

The source code and other files in this directory are part of libtime which
compiles to the binary libraries libtime_trad.a, libtime.a, libctime.a, 
libtime++.a and libtime++.so. This library supports numerical operations 
for dates and times with integer precision down to microseconds.

